## Anti-Patterns (AVOID)

| Pattern | Problem | Correction |
|---------|---------|------------|
| Hiding limitations | Appears evasive | Acknowledge honestly with mitigation |
| Overclaiming | Undermines credibility | Use appropriate hedging |
| Vague future directions | Not actionable | Provide specific 3-tier timeline |
| Missing impact statement | Incomplete conclusion | End with broader significance |
| Repeating Results | Redundant | Synthesize and interpret, don't repeat |

